text.tspan: Creates a workflow that isolates USB devices to one qube and safely
converts, then transfers files to a more trusted "work" qube
Seperate all of your chat clients into one qube, configure all links clicked on
to open in another qube, and route all traffic of both through Tor
Seperate email into one qube while keeping your GPG encryption keys
safely in another offline qube. Also safely converts all attached files
Makes sure all of your web browsing and email activity is routed
through your companies secure VPN (virtual private network).
Recipes are preconfigured "qubes" that make it super simple for any
level of user to benefit from highly configurable & secure Qubes OS
